
1  

Kotemasi ituŋa luka Epuraim ŋes atiar, “Kanukinyo kikonakinia ijo sio kwana, mam ibu konyarau sio nailosio aitiji Midian?” Kitoŋolopata ŋes noi. 
2  Kotema kes atiar, “Eswama anyoika adepar yes? Mere ejokuka luideunos luka imusabibun luka Epuraim adepar luedeŋete luka Abieser? 
3  

Ejaiki Edeke ikapolok luka Midian, Oreb ka Seeb, akanikus: anyoika nuabu eoŋ kapedo aswam adepar yes?” Kosodi konyet anyunyurakec aiŋoŋar, kedau ŋesi einer ŋun.


4  Kobu Gideon Yorodan, kodoka ŋesi ka ituŋa akwat auni luajaas kaŋes, kopasito, konye kodapito. 
5  

Kotema ŋesi ituŋa luka Sukot atiar, “Keŋaiŋait, koinakisi ituŋa lukatupito eoŋ imugatin; naarai epasito, ido adapit eoŋ Seba ka Salumuna, ikabakan luka Midian.” 
6  

Kotemasi ikapolok luka Sukot atiar, “Ejaas kereka akanin nuka Seba ka Salumuna kwana akanikon, tape sio kiinakini ajorekon imugatin?” 
7  Kotema Gideon atiar, “Kanuka ŋun kedau EJAKAIT aijaikin Seba ka Salumuna akanika, apoopoi eoŋ akusiwat kikukwa luka amodiŋ ka ikodokodo.” 
8  

Konyou kanen kolot Penuel, kiner kakes kopone kaŋol; koboŋokis ŋes ituŋa luka Penuel kwape aboŋokinioto ituŋa luka, Sukot. 
9  

Kotema ŋesi ituŋa luka Penuel atiar, “Naaboŋunio kainapakin, atiyaikin etogo lo loeoja noi.”


10  

Ajaas Seba ka Salumuna Karikor, ka ajoresiokec kakes, ituŋa ilukumin itomon ka lukany, ŋul kere luedeuna luka ajore kere naka idwe lukokide: naarai apotu ituŋa ilukumin akwatat ka akaisaarei luautunito ikileŋa kotwakata. 
11  

Kolot Gideon korot loka ŋul kalueboiete koweman kari nakokide naka Noba ka Yogibeka, kodany ajore; naarai etumoro ajore. 
12  

Kokerata Seba ka Salumuna; kodapa kes; kikam ikabakan iarei luka Midian, Seba ka Salumuna, kitubur ajore kere.


13  Koboŋ Gideon okoku loka Yoas kojie anyoun kaneedokarere Keres. 
14  Kikam ŋesi ekatumunan lokituŋa luka Sukot, kiŋit ŋes: kitejen ŋes ikapolok luka Sukot ka imakioke, ituŋa akaisakanykaarei ka lukanykaarei. 
15  Kobu neajaas ituŋa luka Sukot, kotema atiar, “Koanyutu Seba ka Salumuna, lukisekelooto yesi eoŋ ebe, Ejaas kereka akanin nuka Seba ka Salumuna akanikon, tape sio kiinakini ikonituŋa luepasito emugati?” 
16  Koyaŋa imakio lukore, ka ikukwa luka amodiŋ ka ikodokodo, kopoopoia ituŋa luka Sukot. 
17  

Kotiyaik etogo loeoja noi loka Penuel, koar ituŋa lukore.


18  

Kosodi ŋesi atemar Seba ka Salumuna atiar, “Aputos biai ituŋa luiarete yesi koTabor?” Koboŋokis ebe, “Kwape iputor ijo, kesi da kwaŋin; ŋinituŋanan kakesi aputos kidwe luka ekabaka.” 
19  Kotema atiar, “Araas kesi ikainacan, odwe luka totoka; kwape ejaria EJAKAIT, arai kitajarito yesi kes, ti mam eoŋ kaar yes.” 
20  Kotema ŋesi Yeter ekiyaike atiar, “Konyou, koar kes.” Konye mam abu ekatumunan kout ekekileŋ: naarai akuriana, naarai ariŋa erai ekatumunan. 
21  

Kosodete Seba ka Salumuna atemar ebe, “Konyou ijo, koar sio: naarai kwape ejaar etuŋanan, akegogoŋ da ejai kwaŋin.” Konyou Gideon, koar Seba ka Salumuna, koyaŋa apelia nuajaas omurisiŋa luka ikaalaikec.


22  Kosodete ituŋa luka Isirael atemar Gideon atiar, “Koyaai ijo sio, ijo ka okokukon, ka okoku loka okokukon da: naarai kitajar ijo sio kakan naka Midian.” 
23  

Kotema Gideon kes atiar, “Mam akoto ayait yes, karaida okokuka ayait yes: EJAKAIT ŋes kiyai yes.” 
24  

Kotema Gideon kes atiar, “Ejai naakoto ailip yes, koinakinai ŋinituŋanan itetioke luŋatuna.” (Naarai ajaas kes itetio, naarai araas Isimaelin.) 
25  Koboŋokis ebe, “Kiinakini kes ketau kaloejok.” Kopesikis egoe, kocakanakis nen ŋinituŋanan itetioke luŋatuna. 
26  Alaŋiru naka itetio luka esabu luabu kilip arai isekelin

elukumit ka akwat akanykaarei luka esabu; kogelara apelia, ka luidelos, ka inapen lumugeik luanapito ikabakan luka Midian, kogelara da irikoi luajaas omurisiŋa luka ikaalaikec. 
27  

Kiswamau Gideon kes epod,

kibwaik oreke, Opura: kolot Isirael kere ŋina eporo mamakeŋ: koraun do atacit mama ejai Gideon ka ekaleke. 
28  Kwaŋin kitononokata idwe luka Isirael Midian kakonyenekec, mama bobo apotu kikeut akecekwes. Kiyeŋ akwap kapaarasia nuka Gideon.


29  Kolot Yerubaal okoku loka Yoas kiboikin togoke. 
30  

Ajaas Gideon odwe luaurie ŋesi akaisakanykaarei: naarai epu ŋes aŋor. 
31  Abu akebusiat naajai Sekem kourik ŋes esapat, komaik ekekiror Abimelek. 
32  

Kotwana Gideon okoku loka Yoas kedau aibut ejok, kidaikinai ates naka Yoas papake, toma Opura loka Ibieserain.


33  

Kosodi atipet ketwana Gideon, kibelokinos idwe luka Isirael bobo, koloto eporo mama ejaas Ibaalim, kitaraut Baal-berit edekekec. 
34  

Mam idwe luka Isirael apotu kiitut EJAKAIT Ekecedeke, loayuun kes kakanin nuka lukasurupokec kere kaŋoliwai: 
35  

Karaida aikonakin kasianut ekal loka Yerubaal, ŋes Gideon, kwape ejaatar nukajokak kere nuabu ŋesi kikonak Isirael.

